      },
      {
        "name": "ercot_bess_metadata",
        "description": "This table reflects a summary of major parameters associated with each battery storage project available in the ERCOT market. NaN values at any location in the table reflect that the data point is unavailable and not 0. The 'unit_name' column contains a detailed version of each battery project\u2019s name. The 'resource_name', 'resource_name_2', and 'resource_name_3' columns contain codename variations for each battery project. The 'owner' column reflects the company that owns the battery project. The 'capacity_in_mwh', 'latitude', 'longitude', and 'county' columns provide technical and location-specific info. The 'year_online' column shows the year each battery came online. The 'summer_mw', 'winter_mw', and 'capacity_in_mw' columns reflect seasonal and default MW capacity. The 'region' column reflects the zone or hub that the battery belongs to for price mapping. The 'resource_type' column indicates all are storage projects."
      },
